[I] A Binary Linter for security properties, and capabilities in executables

[T] BLint is a Binary Linter to check the security properties, and capabilities
[T] in your executables. Since v2, blint is also an SBOM generator for binaries.

[U] https://github.com/owasp-dep-scan/blint

